

 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * DEPENDENCIES
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Common:
        1) "-std=c++0x" compiler dialect

    Windows:
        1) "-lsetupapi" linker flag
        2) "-static-libgcc -static-libstdc++" linker flags when you use minGw compiler

    Linux:
        1) "-ludev" linker flag
        2) "-lpthread" linker flag

